  "abstract": "The world’s first genetically modified groundnut –\r\ndeveloped by ICRISAT – has reached the field\r\ntrial stage. The new transgenic groundnut\r\ncontains genes for resistance to the peanut clump\r\nvirus (PCV), which is widespread in India and\r\nWest Africa.",
